para_trans: Final Service Seniority List dated 09.01.2025 of Charitable Joint Commissioner, Group A Cadre Officers on Establishment of Charity Commissioner, Maharashtra State, Mumbai.
Government Circular No. CHA-2095 / P.No.86 / Ka. 1
Madam Kama Marg, Martyr Rajguru Chowk,
Reference: - Department of Law & Justice, Government Circular, Serial No. 16.01.2025

The Joint Commissioner of Charities, Maharashtra State, Mumbai, on the establishment of the Commissioner of Charities, Group-A, shall fix the seniority number and date of seniority of the officers of the cadre. Temporary Service Excellence List dated 01.01.2025, Reference No. 1 was published by the Government Circular here. No objection has been received as on date 08.02.2025 in respect of this provisional merit list. Considering this, the present Service Excellence List is being finalised. This final merit list is mentioned in Annexure-A to this circular.

A copy of this Final Service Excellence List is being brought to the notice of all officers of the Charity Joint Commissioner cadre at the establishment of the Charity Commissioner, Maharashtra State, Mumbai.
This Government Circular is available on the www.maharashtra.gov.in website of the Government of Maharashtra.
